And that crooked little man was broken on the wheel</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<p><span class="h2"><strong>10. Syncope Symphony | <a href="/scp-4833">SCP-4833</a>: &quot;The Syncope Symphony&quot;</strong> by Tufto</span><br />
