</blockquote>
<p><span class="h2"><strong>17. Dr. Robert Montauk | <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/tuftos-proposal">Tufto's Proposal</a>: &quot;The Scarlet King&quot;</strong> by Tufto</span><br />
