<p><strong>35.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2420">SCP-2420</a> &quot;A Good Dog&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1345012); return false;">kinchtheknifeblade</a></span></p>
