</blockquote>
<p><strong>39.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1230">SCP-1230</a> &quot;A Hero is Born&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpixel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1350583); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1350583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="MrPixel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1350583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpixel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1350583); return false;">MrPixel</a></span></p>
