<p><strong>43.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1960">SCP-1960</a> &quot;Neptunian Text Messages&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tiger66261" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1373135); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1373135&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="Tiger66261" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1373135)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tiger66261" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1373135); return false;">Tiger66261</a></span> rewritten by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(362048); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=362048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="Smapti" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=362048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(362048); return false;">Smapti</a></span></p>
