<p><strong>44.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1166">SCP-1166</a> &quot;Perfect Lab Specimen&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span> (Original account deleted as seen in the articles history, found this in Helen her metadata.)</p>
