<p><strong>45.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2516">SCP-2516</a> &quot;The Man from Taured&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dododevil" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1854139); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1854139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="DodoDevil" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1854139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dododevil" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1854139); return false;">DodoDevil</a></span></p>
