<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I really needed that. Thanks.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>49.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4274">SCP-4274</a> &quot;The Lonely Angel&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crystalmonarch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2951031); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2951031&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="CrystalMonarch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2951031)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crystalmonarch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2951031); return false;">CrystalMonarch</a></span></p>
