<p><strong>50.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5975">SCP-5975</a> &quot;The Cycle Keeps Spinning&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1777811); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1777811&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609714584" alt="weizhong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1777811)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1777811); return false;">weizhong</a></span></p>
